Personally I think the problem with "Basic" champions is that they have to be purposefully weaker than more "advanced" champions because play input has to match ingame output.

nobody likes being "Outplayed" by a Tryndacrit or "Outplayed" by 1k damage targeted meganuke {{champion:134}} 

Its like If one person had to finish a page full of basic addition vs a person who had to finish a page full of advanced calculus for the same prize. Obviously the person doing the calculus is going to feel cheated.

